| **A01** Broken Access Control | 🔴 | No auth on `/users` |
| **A02** Cryptographic Failures | 🟠 | Email PII exposed in plaintext |
| **A03** Injection | 🟡 | No input parsing yet, but no validation framework in place |
| **A04** Insecure Design | 🟠 | No security middleware pattern |
| **A05** Security Misconfiguration | 🔴 | No helmet, no CORS, hardcoded config, `x-powered-by` leaks |
| **A06** Vulnerable Components | ⚪ | No `package.json` found — cannot audit dependencies |
| **A07** Auth Failures | 🔴 | No authentication at all |
| **A08** Data Integrity Failures | 🟡 | No input validation |
| **A09** Logging Failures | 🔴 | No logging whatsoever |
| **A10** SSRF | ⚪ | Not applicable currently |

