| # | Issue | OWASP | Severity | Effort |
|---|-------|-------|----------|--------|
| 1 | Unauthenticated PII exposure | A01 | 🔴 Critical | Medium |
| 2 | Credentials file in repo | A02 | 🔴 Critical | Low |
| 3 | No security headers | A05 | 🟠 High | Low |
| 4 | No rate limiting | A04 | 🟠 High | Low |
| 5 | No CORS policy | A05 | 🟠 High | Low |
