#### 10. No Request Logging / Audit Trail (OWASP A09: Security Logging & Monitoring Failures)
No request logging means no ability to detect or investigate attacks.

**Fix:**
```js
const morgan = require('morgan');
app.use(morgan('combined')); // or use a structured logger like winston/pino
```

#### 11. No HTTPS Enforcement
The app listens on plain HTTP. In production, TLS should be enforced.

**Fix** (if not behind a reverse proxy):
```js
